title: How To Build a DIY Quarterpipe - Yer Welcome
description:
Ryan Decenzo allows the Yer Welcome crew to take over his backyard and turn it into the best BBQ spot ever! The Yer Welcome crew takes you step-by-step through the build process for Decenzo's new quarterpipe. 
Featuring Dave Bachinsky, Pat Duffy, Sierra Fellers, Mark Appleyard, TJ Rogers, and Ryan Decenzo.
